          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-300"><path d="M69.12,94.15,28.5,128l40.62,33.85a8,8,0,1,1-10.24,12.29l-48-40a8,8,0,0,1,0-12.29l48-40a8,8,0,0,1,10.24,12.3Zm176,27.7-48-40a8,8,0,1,0-10.24,12.3L227.5,128l-40.62,33.85a8,8,0,1,0,10.24,12.29l48-40a8,8,0,0,0,0-12.29ZM162.73,32.48a8,8,0,0,0-10.25,4.79l-64,176a8,8,0,0,0,4.79,10.26A8.14,8.14,0,0,0,96,224a8,8,0,0,0,7.52-5.27l64-176A8,8,0,0,0,162.73,32.48Z"></path></svg></button></div></div><div id="mcp-app-placeholder-toolu_01EoYhSMrcqrZmG6YbfAebuj" class="w-full" style="height: 0px;"></div><div id="mcp-app-container-toolu_01EoYhSMrcqrZmG6YbfAebuj" class="w-full" style=""><div class="h-full w-full"><iframe title="Flask app architecture" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-forms" allow="fullscreen *; clipboard-write *" src="./settings_files/mcp_apps.html" style="width: 100%; border: none; background-color: transparent; height: 767px;"></iframe></div></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Voici l'explication de chaque fonction :</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Initialisation</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">get_db()</code></strong> — Ouvre une connexion MySQL à chaque appel. Utilisée par presque toutes les routes pour accéder à la base <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">nutrition_db</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">send_email()</code></strong> — Envoie un email via Gmail SMTP avec les identifiants du patient (email + mot de passe en clair).</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Routes d'authentification (bleu)</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">POST /login</code></strong> — Connexion patient : vérifie email + mot de passe dans la table <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">patient</code>, retourne nom et prénom si ok.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">POST /loginNut</code></strong> — Même logique mais pour la table <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">users</code> (nutritionniste).</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Routes patients (vert)</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">POST /ajoutep</code></strong> — Insère un nouveau patient avec toutes ses informations médicales dans la table <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">patient</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /allpatient</code></strong> — Retourne la liste complète de tous les patients.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /patientex/&lt;nom&gt;</code></strong> — Recherche un patient par son nom.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /supppatient/&lt;id&gt;</code></strong> — Supprime un patient par son ID.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Routes RDV (orange)</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">POST /prendrerdv</code></strong> — Crée un rendez-vous après avoir vérifié que le créneau (date + heure) n'est pas déjà pris.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /heures/&lt;date&gt;</code></strong> — Retourne la liste des heures déjà réservées pour une date donnée.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /patient</code></strong> — Retourne tous les rendez-vous de la table <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">rdv</code>.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Route email (corail)</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET /accesP/&lt;email&gt;</code></strong> — Récupère les identifiants d'un patient et lui envoie par email via <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">send_email()</code>.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">⚠ Problèmes importants à corriger</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Sécurité</strong> — Les mots de passe sont stockés et envoyés en clair. Il faut utiliser <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">bcrypt</code> ou <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">werkzeug.security</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Méthode HTTP</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/supppatient</code> utilise <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">GET</code> pour supprimer : il faut <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">DELETE</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Clé API exposée</strong> — Le mot de passe Gmail est visible dans le code. Il faut utiliser des variables d'environnement (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.env</code>).</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Connexions non fermées</strong> — Plusieurs routes n'appellent pas <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cursor.close()</code> / <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">db.close()</code> dans un bloc <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">finally</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Tu veux que je corrige un de ces points ?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
